uk.co.saiman.processing

Interface ConfigurableProcessor<C,T,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    C - The configuration interface type
    T - The processing target type
    R - The processing result type

    public interface ConfigurableProcessor<C,T,R>
    Conceptually, a configurable Processor. This interface consumes a given configuration to provide a Processor for that configuration.
